    "summary": "The advocate emphasizes Mark.ai's innovative approach to building AI trust through visual verification, broad applicability across domains, and solid technical implementation using modern technologies. They highlight its scalability potential and clear value proposition. The critic points out limitations including platform dependency, lack of proven metrics, basic implementation, and questions about true innovation, while noting concerns about scalability and missing user validation.",

